Text:
@MrDowntown

The manga is just as amazing as the anime.  The end of the anime deviates a bit from the relative point in the manga, but the anime needed to conclude, so that's to be expected.  The manga still leaves you wanting more, but it also has a good ending that wraps up a few things.  

By the end of the manga I was literally speechless.  I still don't know which ending is better: the anime or the manga.  Both are flawless.
